## AIDE — AI-Driven Development Automation

This project uses AIDE for structured AI-driven development. Run `/aide "<feature description>"` to start the pipeline.

### Workflow

The pipeline follows: requirements → spec → plan → implement → test. Each stage produces artifacts in `.aide/output/`. After each stage, a human gate pauses for confirmation before proceeding.

### Key Commands

- `/aide "<description>"` — Start the full pipeline from the beginning
- `/aide --stage <stage>` — Re-run from a specific stage
- `/aide --continue` — Resume from the last breakpoint

### Configuration

Edit `.aide/config.yaml` to adjust gate types (confirm / confirm_skip / auto) or disable stages.
